import React from 'react'
import { Box, Grid } from '@mui/material'
import { ProjectCard } from '../../components/ProjectCard'
import { Header } from '../../components/Header'

export const LoginProjects = () => {
  return (
    <Box sx={{ backgroundColor: "rgba(0, 145, 136, 0.8)" }}>
      <Header />
      <Grid container direction="row" paddingLeft="3%" paddingTop="2%" justifyContent="space-evenly">
        <Grid item>
          <ProjectCard title={"Minhas Plantas"} maxWidth="330px" description={
            "Aplicação para registrar plantas domésticas e auxiliar com datas de regas, adubação"} />
        </Grid>
      </Grid>
    </Box>
  )
}
